"本文档中的所有模型路径都应调整为您的实际本地路径。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:34
msgid ""
"Qwen3-30B-A3B-W8A8 adopts a hybrid quantization strategy (ordered by "
"model structure):"
msgstr ""
"Qwen3-30B-A3B-W8A8 采用混合量化策略（按模型结构排序）："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:36
msgid "**Embedding layer**: BF16 (no quantization)"
msgstr "**嵌入层**：BF16（未量化）"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:37
msgid "**Q/K normalization** (q_norm, k_norm): BF16"
msgstr "**Q/K 归一化**（q_norm, k_norm）：BF16"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:38
msgid ""
"**Attention projections** (q/k/v/o_proj): Static W8A8 with pre-computed "
"per-tensor scales"
msgstr ""
"**注意力投影**（q/k/v/o_proj）：静态 W8A8，使用预计算的逐张量缩放因子"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:39
msgid "**MoE routing gate** (mlp.gate): BF16"
msgstr "**MoE 路由门控**（mlp.gate）：BF16"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-30B-A3B.md:40
msgid ""
"**MoE expert projections** (gate/up/down_proj): Dynamic W8A8 where input "
"scales are computed on-the-fly during inference"
msgstr ""
"**MoE 专家投影**（gate/up/down_proj）：动态 W8A8，推理过程中实时计算输入缩放因子"

